# ASP.NET Core — backend-specific ignores (root .gitignore also applies)

## User secrets (stored via `dotnet user-secrets` — outside repo, but block local overrides)
appsettings.local.json
appsettings.*.local.json
secrets.json

## Publish / deploy artifacts
publish/
*.pubxml.user

## Rider / ReSharper
_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper
*.DotSettings.user

## Test & coverage
TestResults/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## Local HTTP scratch files with tokens (if you add auth headers later)
*.http.local
